##*******************************************************************************##
###################################################################################

author: Mea


The goal of this project is to create an updated version of the existing
PAD Calculator tool available for free on Google Spreadsheets


goals:
  - integration with data from padherder to easily retrieve user data
  - add support for new features such as multiplayer, eg: user team + friend team

usage:
  - you can use this open source code to create a standalone app if you desire.
      otherwise, I'll create one as soon as I get something barebones working
  - feel free to use and edit, just please give credit
